th="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Tory-Lane.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Jerod-Harris_Getty-Images-for-MCM.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Tory-Lane.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Jerod-Harris_Getty-Images-for-MCM.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Tory-Lane.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Jerod-Harris_Getty-Images-for-MCM-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Tory-Lane.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Jerod-Harris_Getty-Images-for-MCM-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Tory-Lane.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Jerod-Harris_Getty-Images-for-MCM-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Tory-Lane.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Jerod-Harris_Getty-Images-for-MCM-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Tory-Lane.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Jerod-Harris_Getty-Images-for-MCM-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion)</a>因涉嫌通过第三方代理人进行骚扰，正在寻求针对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tory-lanez">托里·拉内兹 (Tory Lanez)</a>的限制令。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/megan-thee-stallion-megan-act-ii-review-3806962">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) – 《梅根：第二幕》评论：这位休斯顿辣妹以一声巨响结束了 2024 年</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位休斯顿说唱歌手周二（12 月 17 日）向洛杉矶高等法院向拉内兹提交了一份限制令申请，拉内兹在 2020 年多次向她开枪。</p><p>去年 8 月，拉内兹因 2020 年 7 月发生的一起事件被判处 10 年监禁，当时梅根在凯莉·詹纳家参加派对时脚部中弹。</p><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-found-guilty-of-shooting-megan-thee-stallion-3371194">被判犯有针对他的所有三项指控</a>：一项使用半自动枪支袭击罪；一项在车内携带隐藏的、已上膛且未注册的枪支的罪名； <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-hit-with-third-charge-in-megan-thee-stallion-trial-3361799">以及一项严重疏忽开枪的指控</a>。这位说唱歌手在狱中坚称自己无罪，并<a href="https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/824266-tory-lanez-small-legal-victory-hip-hop-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener">于今年七月获得了对判决提出上诉的机会</a>。</p><p>据<a href="https://apnews.com/article/megan-thee-stallion-tory-lanez-restraining-order-83e18781439708638a78571b09a070a3" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美联社报道</em></a>，梅根现在声称拉内兹正在监狱中通过第三方代理人骚扰她。一份请愿书称，特哈查皮加州惩教所的监狱通话记录显示，拉内兹一直在协调对她可信度的攻击。</p><p>它强调了多名博主涉嫌代表拉内兹在网上就该案做出虚假陈述，包括他使用的枪和子弹碎片失踪。 </p><figure id="attachment_3803645" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803645" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803645" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion@2000x1270.jpg" alt="梅根·西·种马 (Megan Thee Stallion) 将于 2024 年演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Megan-Thee-Stallion@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803645" class="wp-caption-text"> Megan Thee Stallion 将于 2024 年表演。图片来源：Bryan Bedder/Athlos/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “即使现在，在监狱里，彼得森先生也没有表现出停止的迹象，”它写道。 “尽管彼得森先生因射杀皮特女士而被判处 10 年监禁，但他仍然继续让她遭受反复的创伤和再次受害。”</p><p>请愿书还指出，最初为防止任何先前的骚扰而发布的保护令现已过期。梅根的律师表示，这个漏洞会让受害者面临进一步的困难。</p><p>有关该命令的法庭听证会定于 1 月 9 日举行。</p><p>此前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-sues-youtuber-over-alleged-tory-lanez-lies-and-deepfake-porn-causing-intentional-infliction-of-emotional-distress-3808487">梅根于 10 月对 YouTuber Milagro Gramz 提起诉讼</a>，指控她分享了自己的深度伪造色情内容，并散布了有关这位说唱歌手与拉内兹案件的谎言。该诉讼还指控格拉姆兹（真名米拉格罗·伊丽莎白·库珀）“进行网络跟踪、故意造成情绪困扰和侵犯隐私”。</p><p>上周，梅根在奎因·伊曼纽尔律师事务所的律师随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-accused-of-working-with-youtuber-to-harass-megan-thee-stallion-from-prison-3821909">更新了对库珀的诉讼</a>。律师们透露，他们通过传票获得了拉内兹的入狱电话，证明这位说唱歌手（真名Daystar Peterson）仍在狱中与米拉格罗一起策划针对梅根的骚扰活动。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/25452774-amended-complaint-in-cooper-v/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">娱乐律师兼记者梅根·库尼夫 (Megann Cuniff) 上传的一份法庭文件</a>中，梅根的律师写道：“[库珀]关于审判的虚假陈述是与彼得森的阴谋关系的重要组成部分，其中[库珀]充当付费代理人，用于传播彼得森关于[梅根]的谎言。” </p><figure id="attachment_3795280" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3795280" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3795280" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MEgan@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Megan Thee Stallion 在 2024 年 MTV 音乐录影带颁奖典礼上登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MEgan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MEgan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MEgan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MEgan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MEgan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MEgan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3795280" class="wp-caption-text"> Megan Thee Stallion 在 2024 年 MTV 音乐录影带大奖颁奖典礼上登台表演。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>皮特在她的新纪录片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-announces-new-documentary-in-her-words-3802734"><em>《梅根·西·斯塔林：用她的话来说》</em></a>中公开了这一事件，该纪录片于 10 月份通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">亚马逊 Prime Video</a>发布。</p><p>今年四月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-pens-final-response-on-tory-lanez-trial-people-treated-my-trauma-like-a-running-joke-3433352">皮特对此事件发表了“最终”回应。</a>在回应中，她反思了自己在提出这些指控时所面临的“羞辱”。</p><p>在其他消息中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/twice-music-video-strategy-megan-thee-stallion-3819536">梅根今年第二次与 TWICE 合作，推出了乐观的强力流行歌曲“Strategy”</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-mamushi-remix-featuring-twice-3805692">早在 10 月份，他们就首次合作制作了《Mamushi》的混音版</a>，这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/megan-thee-stallion-megan-album-review-3770938">这位说唱歌手的第三张专辑《Megan》中的热门金曲。</a></p><p> 《Megan》还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995"><em>NME</em> 2024 年 50 首最佳专辑排行榜上排名第 48 位</a>，其第二首单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024-3817596">《Hiss》在 2024 年 50 首最佳歌曲排行榜中排名第十</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-seeking-restraining-order-against-tory-lanez-3823629">Megan Thee Stallion 寻求针对 Tory Lanez 的限制令的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
